{"tid":1472561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集會】香港英國同步集會","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:02.000Z","uid":107572,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6756ab4679e7dafe5397c8fc9b1057a2271b15d","tid":1472561,"uid":107572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2295923657286976&amp;id=2267996923412983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2295923657286976%26id%3D2267996923412983&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=c288f3eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2295923657286976&amp;id=2267996923412983</a><br />\n<br />\n八月十八日<br />\n為香港默哀集會<br />\n倫敦香港同步<br />\n<br />\n時間<br />\n英國中午十二時<br />\n香港晚上七時<br />\n<br />\n英國地點 Trafalgar Square <br />\n香港地點 英國領事館<br />\n<br />\n請手持白色花/白蠟燭為香港法治已死作悼念<br />\n同時為香港人打氣<br />\n<br />\n同時進行BNO轉Bc 聯署<br />\n請支持<br />\n<br />\n如果可以<br />\n參加請留言<br />\n等我地預人數"},{"pid":"b99c3dec9acb437e28cc660132bd133ea1a779f8","tid":1472561,"uid":74432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"當公安逮捕示威者時，我沒有說話，因為我不是示威者。<br />\n當公安逮捕記者時，我沒有說話，因為我不是記者。<br />\n當公安逮捕議員時，我沒有說話，因為我不是議員。<br />\n他們逮捕黑警時，沒有任何一個人可以抗議，因為香港人去曬新彊了。"},{"pid":"98abbe774b791c7f3b61d424045e1cdd9e5009a1","tid":1472561,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0scitm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0scitm.jpg&h=a0de5733&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u05M7mH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu05M7mH.jpg&h=7026b7c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0cba7ead81661e5017e0ea35280de840c9f0f6c","tid":1472561,"uid":161436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6363fd6270799aa6b525de9b896c0b421e6e27c","tid":1472561,"uid":107572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:11:38.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"1419fcd361b5f8b3dbdd303d79eacb1c592b73ac","tid":1472561,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n// The UK should give Hong Kong citizens full UK nationality as a means of reassurance amid the current standoff with Beijing, the chair of the influential Commons foreign affairs committee has argued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=009b6539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"586bcc36ffe971e52dacae64166afc05a8d54a00","tid":1472561,"uid":179293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"🇬🇧❤ Support BNO Hong Konger 🙏🏻非常緊急呼籲：英屬香港人簽署！（廣傳）<br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852 / 000000<br />\n<br />\n#簽署 Sign tick ✅ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=009b6539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"}]}